description: Craving adventure? Pizza? And a the chance to study abroad this summer? Come join the Creative Writing and English Departments, alongside the Study Abroad Office, for an Pizza Meet & Greet to learn about three incredible summer study abroad programs! Whether you're into Shakespeare, fascinated by horror writing, or eager to dive into the world of Irish authors, we've got the perfect summer programs for you. And the best part? You can earn academic credit (3 credits each program) — which could be for your major, minor, or core courses — while exploring the UK and/or Ireland. Join us to discover your perfect program:  Summer: Rutgers-Creative Writing; Where Dips the Rocky Highland Summer: Rutgers-Creative Writing; "Things Terrible and Unguessable" Summer: Rutgers-Shakespeare in England
name: Creative Writing & Study Abroad Pizza Party + Meet and Greet
